{"tid":759272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★響往耀揚？青少年自殺亡人數按年急增五成　逾八成人「從高處墮下」","createTime":"2018-07-28T12:41:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-29T07:17:44.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1f8bf8bb2d3398a258a057d02232c21087ea0ae9","tid":759272,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T12:41:13.000Z","msg":"根據死因裁判庭報告，2017年全年共有916宗自殺死亡個案，自殺率為12.36，即每十萬人就有12.36人自殺亡。<br />\n去年的自殺宗數雖然較2016年的954宗下跌38宗，惟19歲或以下的人士自殺數字卻由2016年的24宗增至去年的36宗，增幅有五成；逾八成自殺青少年選擇「從高處墮下」，香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會形容這個趨勢值得關注。過去曾有年僅7歲兒童求助。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/216070/青少年自殺亡人數按年急增五成-逾八成人-從高處墮下\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F216070%2F%E9%9D%92%E5%B0%91%E5%B9%B4%E8%87%AA%E6%AE%BA%E4%BA%A1%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B8%E6%8C%89%E5%B9%B4%E6%80%A5%E5%A2%9E%E4%BA%94%E6%88%90-%E9%80%BE%E5%85%AB%E6%88%90%E4%BA%BA-%E5%BE%9E%E9%AB%98%E8%99%95%E5%A2%AE%E4%B8%8B&d=dy%2FRrdHMVvVmQJii9%2F0bek%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=2fbec0bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/216070/青少年自殺亡人數按年急增五成-逾八成人-從高處墮下</a>"},{"pid":"87e59d1209563e5dc79da3a04c2cef89c5047a25","tid":759272,"uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T12:41:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/28/204127_9a1cc318f253b11ac63173cc29247234.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F28%2F204127_9a1cc318f253b11ac63173cc29247234.gif&h=9965fae4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/28/204127_00be5daddc3694a4e897bef872a1fbaa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F28%2F204127_00be5daddc3694a4e897bef872a1fbaa.png&h=015ad2da&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a37f835fc52a972bf2e2460f7bae1a5a53f5cbaa","tid":759272,"uid":34685,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"r